t": "Implemented a dedicated test for the active dynamic-access class:\n\n- Added `tests/src/org.hibernate.orm/hibernate-processor/7.2.6.Final/src/test/java/org_hibernate_orm/hibernate_processor/XmlParserHelperTest.java`\n  - Instantiates `XmlParserHelper` through its public constructor.\n  - Calls `getSchema(\"org/hibernate/jpa/orm_3_2.xsd\")`, which reaches `XmlParserHelper.loadSchema(...)`.\n  - This exercises the remaining uncovered `ClassLoader#getResource(String)` call site.\n  - Verifies the schema loads successfully and is cached on repeat lookup.\n\nPer instruction, I did not run or compile the tests locally.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07370612ff1adacf016a353e08c6688193bc91ca2347a94fa9\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 464, "output": 714, "cacheRead": 27136, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 28314, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781874167988, "responseId": "resp_07370612ff1adacf016a353df8d2ac8193962cbfb0c9787af5"}, "toolResults": []}
